=== G-05-clinic: Clinic Visit (B1) ===
Opening: Hello. What brings you in today?

[normal visit]
  IN:  Hi, I need to see a doctor. I have a stomachache.
  OUT: I see. When did the stomachache start?

[short answer]
  IN:  Two days.
  OUT: I see. Have you had a fever or taken any medicine?

[chinese intent]
  IN:  我头疼。
  OUT: 可以这样说："I have a headache." 用 "I have..." 描述症状很自然。How long have you had the headache?

[symptom desc]
  IN:  I ate something bad yesterday.
  OUT: I see. What symptoms are you feeling now?
